# Credit Card Fraud Detection

This project demonstrates a machine learning model for detecting fraudulent credit card transactions. The dataset used is based on real-world financial transaction data, with anonymized features and a target indicating whether a transaction is fraudulent. The goal is to accurately classify transactions as either fraudulent or legitimate.

